Opinion
Pee Curiam,
Order affirmed. See National Grange Mutual Insurance Co. v. Kuhn, 428 Pa. 179, 236 A. 2d 758 (1968) ; Harleysville Mutual Insurance Co. v. Medycki, 431 Pa. 67, 244 A. 2d 655 (1968) ; and Pa. General Insurance Co. v. Barr, 435 Pa. 456, 257 A. 2d 550 (1969).
Mr. Justice Jones dissents.
